Pizza itself wasn’t bad but they never brought the wings and came back with some excuse that soo many people just ordered wings, more than they anticipated. I think they just forgot about it because I didn’t see wings on anyone’s tables. By time the wings got to us we were done eating the pizza and ready to go home. I asked for extra crispy and these wings were wet and soft. Also wouldn’t refill drinks until we finally got someone’s attention and asked for one. I ended up going up to the manager and said we didn’t want the wings(I hadn’t even taken a bite) because it wasn’t extra crispy and we got it way too late. Her response was “really? I even had them cook it two minutes longer” and the “really” was in a condescending tone. Professional! Idk. I know this is a lot and trust me I wanted to like it, but wow they were bad.
